'''''Fatuma''''' (mu ikinamico nka '''''Hadithi za Kumekucha: Fatuma''''' ), ni Filime yikinamico yo muri [[Tanzaniya]] 2018 iyobowe na Yorodani Riber kandi ikaba yarakozwe n’umuyobozi ubwe hamwe n’ababyeyi be; John Riber na Louise Riber<ref>https://www.africaleadftf.org/2018/08/27/usaid-tanzania-supported-film-kumekucha-fatuma-wins-top-swahili-awards-at-2018-zanzibar-film-festival/</ref>.<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt8329296/</ref>  Nibisobanuro bya firime yambere  ''Hadithi za Kumekucha: TUNU'' .  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Beatrice Taisamo mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Ayoub Bombwe na Cathryn Credo mu nshingano zabo<ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/hadithi-za-kumekucha-fatuma/</ref>.

Iyi filime ivuga ku buzima bwo mu cyaro bw’umugore n’umukobwa we aho ahura n’ibibazo byinshi iyo umugabo abangamiye ubuzima bwumukobwa we. Yafatiwe amashusho mu karere ka Arusha muri [[Tanzaniya]]. Iyi filime kandi yayobowe na radiyo 'Kumekucha' yanyuze muri [[Tanzaniya]] muri 2016 na 2017<ref>https://mubi.com/films/fatuma</ref>. 

Iyi filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://staffmeup.com/profile/jordanriber</ref>.  Iyi filime yatsindiye ibihembo bine mu cyiciro cyihariye cya Filime z'Igiswahiri mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Zanzibar 2018 ryerekana amashusho meza<ref>https://www.justdial.com/streaming/watch-movies-online/Hadithi-za-Kumekucha-Fatuma/1594229936744</ref>, Umukinnyi mwiza, Umuyobozi mwiza, na Sinema nziza. Umukinnyi wa filime Catherine Credo yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza naho Jordan Riber yegukana igihembo cyumuyobozi mwiza<ref>https://chicagoreader.com/film/fatuma/</ref>.<ref>https://www.filmhuisdenhaag.nl/agenda/event/fatuma</ref> 

